a little scary ballroom and latin dance has come a long way . even though many of the dancers on the dvd are still at the top ranks of the pro circuit , this is not a great showcase . this is nice to watch in order to compare to the styles and skill of today , but not the kind of video you will watch over and over . the only truly spectacular dancing is that of marcus and karen hilton ( standard only ) . they were then , and are now quite amazing . for those of us in canada , alain doucet and anik jolicouer are on this tape , briefly , in the standard final